本報訊】辯方昨披露現年20多歲的X曾在社交網站剖白，案發後與教練不再親近，每次見面更條件反射地欲後退逃跑，但原來<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">她案發後仍與被告慶祝生日、將兩人合照貼在床尾</span></span></strong>，更形容對方為最佳教練，並將有關資訊從網站刪除。X解釋指事後「一直想當冇事發生」，她認除對被告有戒心外，看上去感情沒變。<br />\n<br />\n辯方出示X已刪除的截圖，包括被告生日照、X寫上「生日快樂」和類似「恆恆」的英文拼音、X出席被告嫁女婚宴的照片、X送給被告波鞋等的禮物照。<br />\n<br />\n主動要求被告教田徑<br />\n<br />\n辯方追問X上載相片的原因，「掛住佢？憎佢？」裁判官亦問：「點解仲要送禮物呢？」X說：「發生之後一直唔想回憶呢件事，想當冇事發生。」<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">辯方則指X明知截圖對辯方案情有利，故她報警後將相片刪除</span></strong></span>，X不同意。X承認案發後仍跟隨被告到大學接受田徑訓練，並坐被告座駕離開，她解釋稱作為運動員不會拒絕教練安排的訓練。辯方又指X多次主動要求被告教導田徑，X直認不諱。  <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180927/20509007\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180927%2F20509007&d=%2FEtv7qlDusZBW5FGm0Xr69tKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=b316b8a6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180927%2F20509007&h=faaf03c7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180927/20509007</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T03:56:48.000Z","msg":"好難令人信佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4f5662979b74a978034dbf83d14a5aac8f5a3d5","tid":838180,"uid":126053,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T03:58:48.000Z","msg":"G"},{"pid":"09f180f6b25a00e8a365d537aced962e5cd0d314","tid":838180,"uid":178205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T03:59:17.000Z","msg":"唔係7年內先告得咩"},{"pid":"9993c2e0d1fd267a3bfdb412fa0885b673808f67","tid":838180,"uid":126053,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T04:00:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/27/120013_4b382224cff3fc7863064f1a84e65d17.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F27%2F120013_4b382224cff3fc7863064f1a84e65d17.png&h=8ccfd84d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3547b72421bbadcee2de7bc3d8b5b717e1bc36da","tid":838180,"uid":182758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T04:03:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://vignette.wikia.nocookie.net/evchk/images/7/74/Th_20100506d980e19b600aea9.gif/revision/latest?cb=20100617142808\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvignette.wikia.nocookie.net%2Fevchk%2Fimages%2F7%2F74%2FTh_20100506d980e19b600aea9.gif%2Frevision%2Flatest%3Fcb%3D20100617142808&h=73cd209a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"43bdb9496e8af393a45760b90b48cba9f5736dfb","tid":838180,"uid":76609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T04:03:47.000Z","msg":"死臭雞"},{"pid":"c902c53dd2dd1ba2d7465e71888490a739d70167","tid":838180,"uid":4525,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T04:07:52.000Z","msg":"判有罪：女權得到彰顯<br />\n判無罪：法治被男權把持"},{"pid":"1e5379c927f77b5f2bfda1834287310ee1510067","tid":838180,"uid":108347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T04:09:38.000Z","msg":"點解唔直接摸閪要陰毛打圈，我睇黎睇去都唔明，想非禮仲要褲都除埋叫佢趴係到點摸都得，係陰毛打圈做咩尻<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 反正佢又冇走冇叫冇反抗"},{"pid":"9f16b2ceb5d7f846141597bc9f62e43dc467636c","tid":838180,"uid":36567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T05:03:41.000Z","msg":"唔係好明打圈呢個動作 有冇示範圖?"}]}